sourceMeaningMnemonic: This <radical>bamboo</radical> can be whittled into an <kanji>example</kanji> of anything. See, here's a <radical>car</radical>. Here's a <radical>snake</radical>. I can make so many examples just with bamboo.
meaningInfo: It's amazing how fast this guy can whittle!
readingMnemonic: One last <kanji>example</kanji> for you. Now I'm going to take this bamboo and whittle it into an example of <reading>Han</reading> (<ja>はん</ja>) Solo!
readingInfo: Han Solo's bamboo example comes to life and runs off.
